title: Margie Singleton - Pledging My Love - Bear Family CD (2013)
description:
Margie Singleton - Pledging My Love - 2013 - Bear Family CD 



One of the great unknowns of the 1950s, Margie Singleton recorded for Starday Records, Mercury Records and United Artists.
She hung around the Louisiana Hayride and recorded with George Jones, Faron Young, and sung back-up on sessions for George Jones, Brook Benton, Clyde McPhatter, Leroy Van Dyke and many others.
A natural singer, Margie Singleton sang on plenty of hit records - but didn't have the hits in her own right.
This CD presents her untold story.
